me Day 即将到来，许多我们最喜欢的小玩意都在打折。自推出以来，Prime Day 一直是一年中以创纪录低价购买耳机、平板电脑、智能手表和其他科技装备的最佳时机之一——当然，如果您是 Prime 会员的话。科技产品的 Prime Day 优惠通常只能与黑色星期五和网络星期一的优惠相匹配，因此现在是购买您感兴趣的大幅折扣设备的好时机。毫无疑问，Prime Day 带来了大量不值得您花时间（更不用说您花钱）的优惠，但我们精选了亚马逊网站，以找到您这次可以获得的最佳科技优惠。以下是您可以在 2023 年获得的最佳亚马逊 Prime Day 电子产品和装备优惠。</p><h2>苹果AirPods Pro </h2><p><core-commerce id="5af865640a3c4e29b36cbb7dfbb8a785" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>苹果第二代<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAQ2WovotMPr9yLYPVXwyANrljUHhEBa9DUXBKVoaTIXT&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-Generation-Cancelling-Transparency-Personalized%2Fdp%2FB0BDHWDR12%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">AirPods Pro</a>在 Prime Day 促销价为 199 美元。这些耳机比前代产品有了巨大的改进，提供了改进的音质、ANC 和透明模式。我们仍然认为它们是<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-wireless-earbuds-120058222.html">iPhone 用户的最佳耳塞，</a>因为它们具有 Apple 特有的功能，例如快速配对和切换以及免提 Siri。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><h2><strong>苹果 AirPods（第 3 代）</strong> </h2><p><core-commerce id="3fb9b761464245c580f93c23d88718af" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>苹果<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJESEI5WThIP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTEzNi0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiYWFkZDA1OTYtMTYwYi00ZWUyLWIyMDQtODEzNmFhYjljZTYzIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAc-_ORonIJOLPMtwwHyjfC_gaJwDOKeTc_-20ZUszcxX&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BDHB9Y8H" data-demonetize-