ildren. If you&#39;re not comfortable giving your kid an iPad, these are decent substitutes.</p><h2>亚马逊 Fire HD 8 </h2><p><core-commerce id="40d82a91a5144de9a7e1666516d0b0fa" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> If you&#39;re on a super tight budget, the <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:20;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDk5WjhITEhUP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFvaC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiZmEyYmU4NTEtNmIzMy00NDQ1LWEyNjgtMDc1ZGM4ZWM2MjU2In0&amp;signature=AQAAAXXq-rwJwUIXV5kFVmRxALsPYPIsifsBeseqQy9oKjC4&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB099Z8HLHT" class="rapid-with-clickid">Fire HD 8</a> is a decent value at $55, which again matches the best price we&#39;ve seen. Normally, this tablet retails around $90. It has a smaller (8-inch) and lower-resolution (1,280x800) display than the Fire HD 10, and it&#39;s not as quick in day-to-day use, but its performance is adequate for the basics, it still gets 10-ish hours of battery life and it&#39;s light in the hand.</p><p> Amazon also makes a <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:21;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDk5WjkzV0Q5Lz90YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby0xb2gtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImZhMmJlODUxLTZiMzMtNDQ0NS1hMjY4LTA3NWRjOGVjNjI1NiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAeZsFN2OmlEmkwa9jG_LX_hh-wQ3F6eUUfT9a61IkWZ7&amp;gcRe